quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  44,40,"Toto inyanga yokhubusia eshina ni ebise biabu biabarererwaho boosi."
  44,41,"Inyanga yomwitsa omukhoonyi shalikhoonya owashie nende shiosishiosi tawe, ne shibalihabinwa tawe."
  44,42,"Halali ulia owa Nyasaye alihelesia tsimbabaasi. Toto ye niwa Amaani, Owobukoosia muno."
  44,43,"Toto omusaala kwa Zaqum."
  44,44,"Ni eshiakhulia shia owetsimbi."
  44,45,"Shinga amafura kasalulusibwe karabachilanga munda."
  44,46,"Shinga okhurabachila khwa amatsi kayile pa."
  44,47,"Baliboolelwa mbu: “Mumutile mana mumusukune hakari womulilo kwa Jahim."
  44,48,"Mana muyombole khumurwe kukwe eshinyasio shia amaatsi karabachilanga."
  44,49,"Pila.. toto (mbu newe welolanga), newe Omwami, Woluyali?"
  44,50,"Toto kano niko kamwakanakanangakhwo.'”"
  44,51,"Toto abaria Nyasaye baliba habundu womulembe."
  44,52,"Mumikunda chomwikulu nende mutsisebele."
  44,53,"Balifwala tsingubo tsinderere tsinyangu tsia hariri..nende tsisiro .. nibahengana."
  44,54,"Endio nilwo lwakaliba, ne khulibabashila mahurul-ain (abakhana bomwikulu)."
  44,55,"Bali laangamwo ebiamo bietsimbia tsioosi nibekhaale nomulembe."
  44,56,"Omo shibalipilamwo lifwa tawe, halali okhufwa khwokhuranga. Ne Nyasaye alibalinda okhurulana nende eshinyasio shia Jahim."
  44,57,"Tsino nitsimbabaasi okhurula khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi, okho nikho okhubura okhukhongo."
  44,58,"Ne efwe khwaikhola (Ikurani) okhuba inyangu khululimi lulwo kho banyoole okhwitsulila."
  44,59,"Kho liinda, bosi toto baliindanga butswa."